page.title: 14CATHERINE'S DAY (MAZE AREA)
page.content: {A day in the life of Catherine }starts at about seven o'clock.I get dressed and make my bed then go down for my breakfast.For my breakfast I get weetabix tea and toast.I wash up when I have finished then I put my coat on and get ready for school.I leave around 8-30 with my friend for school. When I get to school I read until nine o'clock then do some work until 10-20. After break I work until dinner time which is 11-55 to 12-35.At three o'clock I go home and have a light dinner.I go outside to about 7-30 and then I come in and get my little brother ready for bed.I watch some television and then I go outside to about 9-30.When I go in I get my supper and go to bed at about ten o'clock.I read for about an hour before I go to sleep.
